</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="3E1DB66578C65B9EEC81E8B30358AD88" pageId="null" pageNumber="838" type="description">
<paragraph id="6208ED082AA7D743DC14CA7BB1412E39" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="5D9F288C504F98228587EE17A5208BC2" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Minuartia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="838" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="hybrida">
<emphasis id="241F3D0A01C3FD2412745A7C847EE2ED" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">M. hybrida</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 15) durch folgende Merkmale: 5-10 cm hoch, 
<normalizedToken id="B906A8B6586E99C26D148E50B605C9D3" originalValue="drüsig" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">druesig</normalizedToken>
behaart; 
<emphasis id="46F50CAC690B96703838D717A5154752" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">
<normalizedToken id="10990CF975C68C4A5CC0CB255F4B3DD9" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
2-3mm lang; Kapsel etwas 
<normalizedToken id="DC63BC69E2669C2EEDD8AEC1B75C9ADB" originalValue="kürzer" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">kuerzer</normalizedToken>
als die 
<normalizedToken id="26DB2298315B95C744975B4A69D6B472" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
;
</emphasis>
Samen 0,3-0,4 mm lang. - 
<normalizedToken id="3AC8DD47760A5F27FAAE955AF9A61F11" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="499957FE35B271F0DB499D261B79ED50" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="C1A9976CA5C42F37F8612AA1905ABC23" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
und Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6B6020239387FF96D206F52C41172612" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">
<emphasis id="4945128F065CB11DE47B5CC0455F3843" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">Zytologische Angaben. 2n = 46:</emphasis>
Material aus der Slowakei (Favarger 1962a).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D273304FDB1249180114C8EA42984C62" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">
<emphasis id="E222214F2BFF8BD38D3BD80B37DC3AC4" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin und montan. Trockene, sandige 
<normalizedToken id="A226F94356E4D0DB221687AD5DAF3051" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in warmen Lagen. Sandige 
<normalizedToken id="C989B06DD6C956640E9614DA394693FE" originalValue="Plätze" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">Plaetze</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="C3BCFCC5F5582AC5ED0B71D1647B5001" originalValue="Äcker" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">Aecker</normalizedToken>
, Bahnareale.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B7F5BAEE8C61EF4BD46DD486D4CB82F3" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">
<emphasis id="F3B0E094AD952BBDACFD0FB59CF5158B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="EE7AC41B0BA0A658D6F71E933E0EF1B8" originalValue="Osteuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">Osteuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="F8725FB96D26382EA165894E9E35A02B" originalValue="Westwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">Westwaerts</normalizedToken>
vereinzelt bis Wallis, 
<taxonomicName id="A8201869475AE21006600EF1A430E1A9" authority="Pfalz, Harz" authorityName="Pfalz, Harz" class="Liliopsida" family="Melanthiaceae" genus="Paris" kingdom="Plantae" order="Liliales" pageId="null" pageNumber="838" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Paris, Pfalz, Harz</taxonomicName>
; 
<normalizedToken id="479F7B46DB287A8DC1434F60488E71B2" originalValue="nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis 
<normalizedToken id="D42E5647D530299A1A9C0670A6388055" originalValue="Südschweden" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">Suedschweden</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="9EA58B6C7E070AEAB4EAC76335749939" originalValue="Mittelrußland" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">Mittelrussland</normalizedToken>
; 
<normalizedToken id="3E6BFFC7FD7BBC2A3C6A0E49E5C89E39" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Ukraine; 
<normalizedToken id="53DF120110D3507A1B82EAFD3C45341C" originalValue="südwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">suedwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Alpen, 
<normalizedToken id="8A561638D9471EF63C947FD5F529803A" originalValue="südliche" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">suedliche</normalizedToken>
Balkanhalbinsel, Schwarzes Meer; Kleinasien (?), Kaukasus (?), Persien (?). Verbreitungskarte von Meusel (1964). - Im Gebiet: Wallis (auch 
<normalizedToken id="65246F631527262A713D0C2CE8D85E32" originalValue="Simplonsüdseite" pageId="null" pageNumber="838">Simplonsuedseite</normalizedToken>
), Aostatal; selten.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
